high_descs: Move forward to the trash can.
Pick up the bar of soap from the trash can.
Hold the bar of soap and turn around then left and find the right side sink.
Place the soap on the counter, in between the two sinks.
Take a few steps to the left and face the sink.
Pick up the soap from the left side of the counter.
Carry the soap and move a few steps right.
Place the soap on the right side of the counter.
anns.task_desc: Move two bars of soap to the counter.

high_descs: Turn slightly left and go to the can in the corner.
Pick up the soap in the can.
Turn around and turn left at the shower and go to the sink.
Put the soap on the counter to the right of the bottle.
Turn left, go to the toilet and turn right in front of it.
Pick up the soap on top of the toilet.
Turn right and walk toward the shower and turn left in front of the sink.
Put the soap on the closest right corner.
Walk forward to face the trash can in the corner of the room.
Pick up the bar of soap in the trash can on the floor.
Turn around and walk across the room to face the sink.
Place the bar of soap on the counter next to the sink.
Turn left and walk forward and turn to the right to face the toilet.
Pick up the bar of soap on the back of the toilet.
Turn right and walk forward and turn right to face the sink
Place the bar of soap next to the first bar of soap on the sink.
anns.task_desc: To move two bars of soap to next to the sink.
